<!-- ============ HEADER (shared shell) ============ -->

<!-- ============ HERO ============ -->
<section class="hero">
  <Svg19 class="botan hero-botan-tl" aria-hidden="true" />
  <Svg20 class="botan hero-botan-br" aria-hidden="true" />
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <p class="eyebrow">Zuo Yue Zi Meal Plan</p>
    <h1>Classic Meal</h1>
    <p class="cn-title">精緻月子餐</p>
    <p class="hero-sub">Warm. Balanced. Reassuring.</p>
    <p class="lede">Your body just did something extraordinary. For the next thirty days, the only decision you should have to make at mealtime is <em>when to eat</em>.</p>
    <p class="hero-price"><span class="from">30 days · 3 meals a day</span>{usd(products.local_classic_30d.price)}</p>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a href="#pricing" class="btn btn-primary">See what's included</a>
      <a href="#taste" class="btn btn-ghost">Try a taste first</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- HERO BANNER IMAGE — replace with a wide, warm hero shot of a full Classic meal spread (~1600×640) -->
  <div class="hero-banner reveal">
    <div class="img-slot">
      <!-- <img src="images/classic-hero.jpg" alt="A full Classic Meal spread — soups, chicken, rice and vegetables"> -->
      <span class="slot-icon">❀</span>
      <span class="slot-label">Hero Image</span>
      <span class="slot-hint">Wide, warm shot of a full Classic meal spread · ~1600 × 640</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ OPENING ============ -->
<section class="opening">
  <div class="narrow reveal">
    <p>If you're wondering whether you really need a meal plan — whether you couldn't just cook, or let family bring things over — it's a fair question. Plenty of mothers ask it.</p>
    <p>Then week two arrives. The baby is feeding every two hours. You haven't slept a full night since the hospital, and the person standing in front of the open fridge at 3 p.m., trying to remember whether she's eaten today, is you.</p>
    <p class="pull">Zuo Yue Zi has a simpler answer: someone else cooks, and you recover. That is the whole tradition, and it's the whole plan.</p>
    <p>The Classic Meal plan takes the guesswork out of postpartum healing, delivering the power of Zuo Yue Zi through warm soups, nourishing proteins, and restorative herbs. No prepping. No Googling "what should I eat after birth" at midnight. Just comforting meals that feel like Mom's, cooked from scratch and delivered to your door — every day, for a full month.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="floral-divider reveal">
  <span class="line"></span>
  <Svg21 aria-hidden="true" />
  <span class="line r"></span>
</div>

<!-- ============ DAILY ============ -->
<section class="daily" id="daily">
  <Svg22 class="botan daily-botan" aria-hidden="true" />
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">What Arrives Every Day</p>
      <h2>Daily healing, without the hassle</h2>
      <p>Every day of your thirty days, you'll enjoy:</p>
    </div>
    <div class="daily-grid reveal">
      <div class="daily-cell">
        <!-- IMAGE — a warming soup / broth dish (~600×400) -->
        <div class="img-slot"><span class="slot-icon">❀</span><span class="slot-label">Dish Photo</span><span class="slot-hint">A warming soup or broth · ~600 × 400</span></div>
        <div class="cell-body">
          <div class="num"><span>一</span></div>
          <h3>Three comforting meals</h3>
          <p>Balanced the traditional way to restore strength, energy, and gut health — soups, slow braises, gentle vegetables, and nourishing rice dishes, in the sequence your recovery follows.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="daily-cell">
        <!-- IMAGE — sesame oil chicken or a braise (~600×400) -->
        <div class="img-slot"><span class="slot-icon">❀</span><span class="slot-label">Dish Photo</span><span class="slot-hint">Sesame oil chicken or a braise · ~600 × 400</span></div>
        <div class="cell-body">
          <div class="num"><span>二</span></div>
          <h3>Warm, cooked-from-scratch dishes</h3>
          <p>Nothing pre-packaged, nothing shortcut. Every dish is built on hours of slow simmering and warming ingredients that support postpartum circulation and gentle recovery.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="daily-cell">
        <!-- IMAGE — a neatly plated daily meal set (~600×400) -->
        <div class="img-slot"><span class="slot-icon">❀</span><span class="slot-label">Dish Photo</span><span class="slot-hint">A plated daily meal set · ~600 × 400</span></div>
        <div class="cell-body">
          <div class="num"><span>三</span></div>
          <h3>A nourishing rhythm</h3>
          <p>Breakfast, lunch, dinner — arriving like clockwork so your body feels seen, supported, and steady, even on the days when everything else feels upside down.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ GALLERY ============ -->
<section class="gallery" id="gallery">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">On the Table</p>
      <h2>A look at the food</h2>
      <p>Real dishes from a Classic week.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="gallery-grid reveal">
      <!-- IMAGE — hero dish, tall (~800×880) -->
      <div class="img-slot"><span class="slot-icon">❀</span><span class="slot-label">Feature Dish</span><span class="slot-hint">Tall hero dish · ~800 × 880</span></div>
      <!-- IMAGE — square (~520×440) -->
      <div class="img-slot"><span class="slot-icon">❀</span><span class="slot-label">Dish</span><span class="slot-hint">~520 × 440</span></div>
      <!-- IMAGE — square (~520×440) -->
      <div class="img-slot"><span class="slot-icon">❀</span><span class="slot-label">Dish</span><span class="slot-hint">~520 × 440</span></div>
      <!-- IMAGE — square (~520×440) -->
      <div class="img-slot"><span class="slot-icon">❀</span><span class="slot-label">Dish</span><span class="slot-hint">~520 × 440</span></div>
      <!-- IMAGE — square (~520×440) -->
      <div class="img-slot"><span class="slot-icon">❀</span><span class="slot-label">Dish</span><span class="slot-hint">~520 × 440</span></div>
    </div>
    <p class="gallery-note">Menus rotate across the thirty days to follow the recovery sequence.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="floral-divider reveal">
  <span class="line"></span>
  <Svg21 aria-hidden="true" />
  <span class="line r"></span>
</div>

<!-- ============ PERSONA ============ -->
<section class="persona">
  <Svg23 class="botan persona-botan" aria-hidden="true" />
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="persona-grid reveal">
      <div class="persona-left">
        <p class="eyebrow">Perfect For You If…</p>
        <h2>You focus on the baby. We handle the rest.</h2>
        <p>The Classic Meal is for the mom who wants complete daily support without having to think about food. Three meals a day, warm and ready.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="persona-right">
        <p>Maybe you're a first-time mom craving structure amid the chaos — a rhythm you can count on when nothing else has one yet. Or a seasoned mom who already knows that good food and low stress matter most this time around.</p>
        <p>Maybe you grew up hearing about Zuo Yue Zi and you're balancing tradition with modern life — looking for meals that honor your roots but fit the way you actually live. Or maybe you simply want to feel <em>nourished, cared for, and less overwhelmed</em>.</p>
        <p>Whatever your journey, these meals exist to support your recovery — so you can focus on bonding, healing, and being fully present with your baby.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ QUOTE ============ -->
<section class="quote-band">
  <div class="stamp-wm" style="top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%)"></div>
  <div class="quote-mark">"</div>
  <div class="quote-inner reveal">
    <p class="eyebrow">Moms Say</p>
    <p class="q">"It felt like having someone quietly take care of me behind the scenes."</p>
    <p class="by">— A Classic Meal mom</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ ADD-ONS ============ -->
<section class="addons" id="addons">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Make It Yours</p>
      <h2>Two ways to go deeper</h2>
      <p>The Classic plan is complete on its own. These add-ons are here if you want more.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="addon-grid reveal">
      <div class="addon-card">
        <!-- IMAGE — a cup of chicken essence (~760×400) -->
        <div class="img-slot"><span class="slot-icon">❀</span><span class="slot-label">Add-on Photo</span><span class="slot-hint">A cup of chicken essence · ~760 × 400</span></div>
        <div class="addon-body">
          <p class="tag">Recovery Booster</p>
          <h3>Slow-Simmered Chicken Essence</h3>
          <p class="cn">熬雞精</p>
          <p>Your go-to recovery booster — slowly simmered for hours from <strong>aged hens and white-feather chickens</strong> until every drop is rich with collagen, protein, and minerals, then concentrated into one small, warming cup.</p>
          <p>Easy to sip on the days you're too tired for a full meal, it arrives ready to warm — no cooking, no cleanup. Mothers who add it tend to keep it for the whole month.</p>
          <p class="addon-price">{usd(products.chicken_essence.price)} / serving · add on whenever you like</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="addon-card">
        <!-- IMAGE — herbal drinks / packets (~760×400) -->
        <div class="img-slot"><span class="slot-icon">❀</span><span class="slot-label">Add-on Photo</span><span class="slot-hint">The daily herbal drinks · ~760 × 400</span></div>
        <div class="addon-body">
          <p class="tag">Herbal Add-On</p>
          <h3>The 30-Day Herbal Drinks</h3>
          <p class="cn">月子藥膳</p>
          <p>The daily herbal drinks that have anchored Chinese postpartum recovery for generations — <strong>15 formulas</strong> that follow the traditional recovery sequence, stage by stage across your thirty days.</p>
          <p>Add them to your Classic plan by the day — as few or as many as you like. Prefer them every single day of your recovery? The <strong>Herbal Meal plan</strong> already includes the full 30 days.</p>
          <p class="addon-price">{usd(products.herbal_drink.price)} / day · add any number of days</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="floral-divider reveal">
  <span class="line"></span>
  <Svg21 aria-hidden="true" />
  <span class="line r"></span>
</div>

<!-- ============ PRICING ============ -->
<section class="pricing" id="pricing">
  <Svg24 class="botan pricing-botan" aria-hidden="true" />
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Choose Your Length</p>
      <h2>One plan, your timeline</h2>
      <p>Three warm meals a day, delivered fresh daily. Pick the length that fits your recovery.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="price-grid reveal">
      <div class="price-card">
        <p class="mode">Every Day Includes</p>
        <h3>Classic Meal</h3>
        <p class="cn">精緻月子餐</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Breakfast</strong> — egg &amp; porridge</li>
          <li><strong>Lunch</strong> — fish soup or lunch soup, entrée, vegetables, rice &amp; grains</li>
          <li><strong>Dinner</strong> — Taiwanese postpartum soup, dinner soup, entrée, vegetables, rice &amp; grains</li>
          <li><strong>2 desserts</strong> + a daily healing drink</li>
          <li>Warm, cooked-from-scratch Zuo Yue Zi dishes, delivered fresh daily</li>
        </ul>
        <a href={orderUrl('local_classic', locale)} class="btn btn-primary">Order online</a>
      </div>
      <div class="price-card">
        <p class="mode">Pricing</p>
        <h3>By Length</h3>
        <p class="cn">依天數計費</p>
        <div class="tier-row feat"><span class="d">30 Days</span><span class="p">{usd(products.local_classic_30d.price)}</span></div>
        <div class="tier-row"><span class="d">21 Days</span><span class="p">{usd(products.local_classic_21d.price)}</span></div>
        <div class="tier-row"><span class="d">14 Days</span><span class="p">{usd(products.local_classic_14d.price)}</span></div>
        <div class="tier-row"><span class="d">1 Day</span><span class="p">{usd(products.local_classic_1d.price)}</span></div>
        <p class="dep">14–30 day plans: {usd(deposits.standard)} deposit · balance within 3 days of first delivery. 1-day: paid in full.</p>
        <a href={orderUrl('local_classic', locale)} class="btn btn-ghost">Order online</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="pricing-foot">Not sure which length fits? Call us at <a href={`tel:${phones.main}`}>{phoneDisplay(phones.main)}</a> — we're happy to talk it through, no pressure.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ DOWNLOADS (shared block — reuse on every product page) ============ -->
<section class="actions" id="resources">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Review At Your Own Pace</p>
      <h2>Download the details</h2>
      <p>Prefer to look things over on your own? Grab the order form, compare every plan side by side, or browse the full menu.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="action-downloads reveal">
      <a href="https://file.jingmommy.com/f/Main_Order_Form.pdf" class="action-btn">
        <Svg25 class="ico" />
        <span class="lbl"><span class="en">Order Form <span class="pdf-tag">PDF</span></span><span class="cn">下載訂購單</span></span>
      </a>
      <a href="https://file.jingmommy.com/f/Meal_Comparison_Chart.pdf" class="action-btn">
        <Svg26 class="ico" />
        <span class="lbl"><span class="en">Meal Comparison Chart <span class="pdf-tag">PDF</span></span><span class="cn">餐點對照表</span></span>
      </a>
      <a href="https://file.jingmommy.com/f/Menu.pdf" class="action-btn">
        <Svg27 class="ico" />
        <span class="lbl"><span class="en">Full Menu <span class="pdf-tag">PDF</span></span><span class="cn">菜單</span></span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ UPGRADE ============ -->
<section class="upgrade">
  <div class="upgrade-inner reveal">
    <p class="eyebrow">Want the Full Tradition?</p>
    <h2>Upgrade to the Herbal Meal plan</h2>
    <p>Everything in the Classic — plus the 30-day herbal drinks included, a soothing daily ritual rooted in traditional Chinese medicine, designed to nourish, restore, and strengthen from within.</p>
    <a href={route("/plans", locale)} class="btn btn-primary">Explore the Herbal Meal — {usd(products.local_herbal_30d.price)}</a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ FAQ ============ -->
<section class="faq-band" id="faq">
  <Svg28 class="botan faq-botan" aria-hidden="true" />
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Good Questions</p>
      <h2>Before you decide</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-list reveal">
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What's the difference between Classic and Herbal?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Both plans deliver three full recovery meals a day from the same kitchen, cooked the same way. The Herbal Meal plan additionally includes the 30-day herbal drinks — the traditional daily herbal drink that follows the recovery sequence. On the Classic plan, you can add the herbal drinks anytime for {usd(products.herbal_drink.price)}/day.</p></div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Will I like the food if I didn't grow up with it?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Most first-timers tell us the food is warmer and more familiar than they expected — savory broths, slow-cooked chicken, gentle vegetables, comforting rice dishes. The easiest way to know for sure is to <a href={route("/sample", locale)}>try a sample day</a> before committing.</p></div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How does delivery work?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>In our regular service area, meals are delivered fresh every day and we aim to reach your door before noon — though actual times can shift with traffic and routes, so an exact hour isn't guaranteed. Remote areas receive every-other-day delivery, delivery times there can't be guaranteed, and an additional delivery fee may apply. Refrigerate your meals when they arrive, and heat them thoroughly before eating.</p></div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>When should I order?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>At least one month before your due date, if you can. The week your baby arrives, you will not have the bandwidth to compare plans or fill out forms — and you shouldn't have to. Your start date can be adjusted once the baby comes.</p></div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ TASTE CTA ============ -->
<section class="taste" id="taste">
  <Svg29 class="botan taste-botan-l" aria-hidden="true" />
  <Svg30 class="botan taste-botan-r" aria-hidden="true" />
  <div class="taste-inner reveal">
    <p class="eyebrow">Not Sure Yet?</p>
    <h2>Taste before you commit.</h2>
    <p>Most mothers who choose the Classic plan tried a sample first. Have a full day of meals delivered — and let the food make the case.</p>
    <div class="taste-cta">
      <a href={route("/sample", locale)} class="btn btn-primary">Order a sample day</a>
      <a href={route("/contact", locale)} class="btn btn-ghost">Contact us</a>
    </div>
    <p class="taste-note">Or call {phoneDisplay(phones.main)} — we're usually around later than you'd expect.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ FOOTER (shared shell) ============ -->

<script is:inline>
(function(){
  var els=document.querySelectorAll('.reveal');
  if(!('IntersectionObserver' in window)){els.forEach(function(e){e.classList.add('in')});return;}
  var io=new IntersectionObserver(function(entries){
    entries.forEach(function(en){
      if(en.isIntersecting){en.target.classList.add('in');io.unobserve(en.target);}
    });
  },{threshold:0.12,rootMargin:'0px 0px -40px 0px'});
  els.forEach(function(e){io.observe(e);});
  document.querySelectorAll('#nav a').forEach(function(a){
    a.addEventListener('click',function(){document.getElementById('nav').classList.remove('open');});
  });
})();
</script>
</Page>
